# === TRIPLE-235 ROUND-NUMBER LANDMARK · 173rd AXIS CLOSED =================
# ============================================================================
# Axis position: TS-Node=235 CLOSES Axis 180 at slot 1/1/1 — quadruple-clean
# closure of the canonical pure-language syntax highlighting library
# ecosystem spanning the three major systems languages.  All three lanes
# anchor on a single pure-host-language syntax highlighter by a single
# recognized maintainer that reads industry-standard grammar files
# (Sublime Text `.sublime-syntax`, Pygments lexer modules, or VS Code
# TextMate `.tmLanguage.json` grammars):
